title: popovers

needs:
 - 2 eggs
 - 250ml milk
 - 140g flour (1 cup, 4 ½ oz, 130g)
 - ½ tsp salt

steps:
 - preheat oven to 200°C.
 - whisk the eggs.
 - whisk in the milk.
 - mix in the flour & salt.
 - pour into muffin cups.
 - bake for 25 minutes.
 - pierce the top of each popover to release the steam.
